

	 
       Wedding Letter   Congratulations to one of the best days of your lives.  I am happy to have met and known two imperfect persons who came together and became the perfect couple for each other.  Syempre alam nyo na siguro na there should be compromise =).  It's interesting to note how this sounds good coming from me, but a bad idea when the person giving the advice is in that situation.  Ito ay sinulat ko sa fifth floor ng Edsa Shang habang umiinom ng mango-kiwi shake from Big Chill (order kayo) kasi bawal uminom sa mrt.  Nabanggit ko kay mommy na bukod sa ikakasal kayo ay meron pang dalawa na officemate ko rin: si Roger at Arnie.  Naisip ko tuloy na baka isipin ni mommy na gusto ko na rin lumagay sa tahimik.  Ayoko pang mamatay.  Did they not say that marriage is suicide? 
     
    
